gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afb45aa43d78c92f23a9d1fa26eb99026b734c7a","tid":1733714,"uid":181531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:56:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47d07bfa4bb048019a15e628102ba3bca29573e6","tid":1733714,"uid":151314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:56:52.000Z","msg":"Poly嘅同學起入面live舉美國旗叫救命有冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我知好柒<br />\n但可能有用呢<br />\n上次都係舉旗先有今日嘅民主人權法案）雖然未過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\nBtw<br />\n出面嘅戴美國旗唱美國國歌呼籲人道援助可行嗎？"},{"pid":"d49af9f376b8cf2813e9f7e3ee41ac19d955208e","tid":1733714,"uid":248394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:57:26.000Z","msg":"【讀者分享】<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=145833756821455&amp;id=119376019467229&amp;anchor_composer=false\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D145833756821455%26id%3D119376019467229%26anchor_composer%3Dfalse&d=uhXF1s3LJRzyxl6IDZpy2Te9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=8ac1b953\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=145833756821455&amp;id=119376019467229&amp;anchor_composer=false</a><br />\n<br />\n恐怖分子正挾持人質上東鐵線<br />\n<br />\n搵人mon實粉嶺上水往羅湖方向月台<br />\n逢係有列車經過都要準備錄影<br />\n就算佢冇話不停站都係<br />\n<br />\n一旦越過粉嶺界線<br />\n手足請準備以 all means necessary 制止佢哋越過上水<br />\n請以任何手段阻止恐怖分子挾持人質逃離現場<br />\n<br />\n可以嘅話東鐵沿線到放人監視<br />\n但係最緊要係係粉嶺哨站<br />\n上水死線攔截<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n手動傳"},{"pid":"7f8c89699c6a0282405ce3e23454c2c6b80d7f5e","tid":1733714,"uid":70686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:58:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"41e4